## ✅ Step 2: Confirm `LICENSE` File

You've already uploaded the `LICENSE` file — perfect!  
Make sure it's in your root folder and is valid (MIT, BSD, etc.).

---

## ✅ Step 3: Check `pubspec.yaml`

Here’s a clean version — make sure your file looks like this:

```yaml
name: prayer_times_helper
description: A simple package to get today's Islamic prayer times and next prayer info.
version: 1.0.0
homepage: https://github.com/Muhaiminkpm/prayer_times_helper
repository: https://github.com/Muhaiminkpm/prayer_times_helper
environment:
  sdk: '>=3.3.0 <4.0.0'

dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter

# No need to list your own package here
